articles.author: Jenni Reid, Holly Ellyatt
articles.title: European stocks cautiously higher as investors hope volatility has passed - CNBC
articles.description: European markets were higher on Tuesday as investors in the region continue to hope that recent market volatility has come to an end.
articles.content:
European stock markets were higher Tuesday, continuing positive momentum as investors in the region hope that recent market volatility has come to an end.
